{"tid":1633793,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解男朋友唔肯帶我見家長？","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:11:30.000Z","uid":272006,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7010e713c0811041b500332677b9a0c20e3e93d7","tid":1633793,"uid":272006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"拍咗拖差唔多有一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男朋友一直都唔想俾佢爸媽知佢拍拖 話唔想麻煩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />莫講話上屋企見家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次上佢屋企都要偷偷摸摸甘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話唔可以俾佢屋企人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連佢啲朋友都未見過 甚少公開我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我每次同佢一齊果時都覺得好似唔見光甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪因為覺得有我哩個女朋友好失禮佢？定係因為未認得我所以唔想公開我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[red]有冇巴絲打可以解答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[red]</span>"},{"pid":"6dd6d5dd6772bfcfe3a6fbd0004ed17cbf511adc","tid":1633793,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"唔識字真係好失禮啊！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"aa902e49b80dadec3c524c6e65b92df7cb4fea31","tid":1633793,"uid":291167,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:43.000Z","msg":"其實你係唔係真嘅女朋友？最怕你係做咗小三都唔知，男嘅唔會怕帶女友見家人，除非唔唔想咁快帶返去，但你又上過佢屋企，但好似係偷偷摸摸，純粹當你係炮友？<br />\n女仔應該有所堅持，真心愛你嘅男仔一係未準備好帶返去，一係就直接返屋企一齊吃飯。"},{"pid":"b3113e537015b24ab154c6088af7c1f3ab06a3f3","tid":1633793,"uid":51753,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"帶你番屋企同你介紹<br />\nhi 呢個我老婆呀 呢個我個女 4歲<br />\n叫姐姐啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 姐姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 乖"},{"pid":"ecc66de2db52e750d33d0e846f25606318af763e","tid":1633793,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3113e537015b24ab154c6088af7c1f3ab06a3f3","tid":1633793,"uid":51753,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"帶你番屋企同你介紹<br />\nhi 呢個我老婆呀 呢個我個女 4歲<br />\n叫姐姐啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 姐姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 乖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1949aa91e83b7006af80085fc41b1ef4c83770ee","tid":1633793,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"佢幾歲？<br />\n可能未到結婚階段唔想搞咁多野"},{"pid":"fccddb321650835d9a7cf797d96b5986381744a9","tid":1633793,"uid":182430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"連係屋企傾電話都要偷偷摸摸<br />\ni know that feel"},{"pid":"31b51618909fbbe6e672a1f4c457d8e199b360f0","tid":1633793,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"